quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"A wid iumnen! £uôwat a kwen ssbaâden, af usmekti n Öebbi, wayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen! Wid igan akka, ihi, widak d imexsuôen"
  63,10,"Ssedqet seg wayen i wen Nefka, uqbel a d tas tmeppant ar yiwen degwen, ad yini: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer ad iyi Teswexxôev ar lajel aqôib, ad seddqe$, ad ili$ seg wid imaânen"
  63,11,"Ur Irennu Öebbi di laâmeô, d awez$i, ma iusa d lajel is. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem"